    "name": "SteamWorld Heist II",
    "steam_appid": 2396240,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 海浪之下危机四伏——一场水资源危机正在酝酿！不知为何，这种宝贵的资源开始变得致命，腐蚀着金属肢体和机械心脏。作为传奇一般的Leeway船长，你和你那群乌合之众的Steambot船员需要下定决心，找到这一威胁的来源，并在形势无可挽回之前拯救整个机器族！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/0a7156f42a52c60e114aea24df695947.avif?t=1759330639\" width=601 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/0274792e00f910e7b1a74016dc98393b.poster.avif?t=1759330639\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/0274792e00f910e7b1a74016dc98393b.webm?t=1759330639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/0274792e00f910e7b1a74016dc98393b.mp4?t=1759330639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>回合制策略游戏的最佳状态</strong> <br>沉浸在经过升级的策略游戏体验之中——以深受喜爱的《蒸汽世界大劫掠》游玩机制为基础加以打造的游戏体验。在你谋划自己的回合、安排船员位置和仔细瞄准每一次射击的过程中，每一步都至关重要。让子弹借助墙壁反弹，并利用所处环境来智取敌人，但要记住——胜利最青睐的是思路周密的策略，而非条件反射般的快枪手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/2a6109c630ccf30aaa800910512cbaf2.avif?t=1759330639\" width=601 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/4cbb180e220d1d5694ab00dc19bd037d.poster.avif?t=1759330639\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/4cbb180e220d1d5694ab00dc19bd037d.webm?t=1759330639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/4cbb180e220d1d5694ab00dc19bd037d.mp4?t=1759330639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新的水域，新的冒险</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >乘坐你值得信赖的潜水艇，跨越浩瀚的海洋。直面实时海战挑战，带领你的船员接受船对船策略战斗的洗礼，同时发现每一波浪潮之中的隐藏宝藏。作为船长，你的决定将会塑造在整个浩瀚之海中的旅程。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/0a30b5c04a2ce6866762b4fbbdc6698f.avif?t=1759330639\" width=601 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/050fe3fac36898447dc41e45fe9bb142.poster.avif?t=1759330639\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/050fe3fac36898447dc41e45fe9bb142.webm?t=1759330639\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/050fe3fac36898447dc41e45fe9bb142.mp4?t=1759330639\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自定义你的船员，随心所欲</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >凭借超过150种武器、实用物品和船只升级，船员自定义的可能性趋近于无限。针对各种策略装备你的Steambot——无论你偏好的是枪法出众的狙击手，还是挥舞大锤的搏击手。解锁新的船员、职业、技能和装备，为每项任务完善你的团队。<br><br><strong>徜徉在手工制作的世界之中</strong><br>全身心沉浸在一个手工制作的美丽世界中，其中充斥着独特的环境、乖张的角色以及一个引人入胜的故事。是的，没错，Steam Powered Giraffe带着全新的配乐荣誉回归，这段美妙的旋律将会在你停靠好船只之后久久伴随着你。此外，凭借30小时以上的通关时间，你的冒险之旅将如这片海洋本身一般宽广！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/4e451c0520320faf560e475f23e2b21e.avif?t=1759330639\" width=601 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >比拼精准度的回合制战斗，支持令人愉悦的跳弹机制 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >发现广袤的世界，其中充斥着实时海战和隐藏宝藏 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助超过150种武器、物品和升级自定义你的船员 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索丰富的新职业系统，打造符合你的游玩风格的船员 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一次令人心旷神怡的新冒险，背景设定在蒸汽世界宇宙中，通关时间超过30小时 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐出自游戏迷最爱的Steam Powered Giraffe！<br><br>整个机器族的命运掌握在你手上——准备好带领你的船员穿越暗藏危险的水域了吗？ <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2396240/extras/c6cc9c3a2810b57a3a4a8e93b6383442.avif?t=1759330639\" width=601 height=442 /></span></p></li></ul>",
